        "discriminators": [
          "The middle of the bell size ladder, and size is the only real axis: brighter and shorter-ringing than BELLS-LARGE, darker and longer-ringing than the tiny BELLS-ANIMAL. Rung by hand, so several clapper strikes usually appear in one file.",
